climate change and Susan Sontag on metaphor, speculative fiction and Succession.Avowedly ambivalent about Franzen, Gibson offers both a fresh appreciation of the author’s work and a searching critical analysis of his pronouncements on the novel’s fate. Wide-ranging and stylistically ambitious, Freedom Reread delivers an assured, artful inquiry into Franzen’s novelistic technique and public persona.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Books & Reading.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertColumbia University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311074967008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Cultural and Area Studies 2023 Englishz978311131909408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Cultural and Area Studies 2023z97831113181270 cprintz978023118892040uhttps://doi.org/10.7312/gibs1889240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780231548076423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780231548076/original  a978-3-11-074967-0  Columbia University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-131812-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Cultural and Area Studies 2023b2023  a978-3-11-131909-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Cultural and Area Studies 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2023